N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4102.2 - Attempted violations

State Regulations

Any attempt to violate any of the rules and regulations
of the commission falling short of actual accomplishment, shall constitute an
offense and shall be punishable as if consummated. Notes
